Au_{xx} + Bu_{xy} + Cu_{yy} = 0
B^2 - 4AC < 0
A\lambda^2+B\lambda+C
C\lambda^2+B\lambda+A
\mathbb{C}
A\lambda^2+B\lambda+C=A\left(\lambda+\dfrac{B+\sqrt{B^2-4AC}}{2A}\right)\left(\lambda+\dfrac{B-\sqrt{B^2-4AC}}{2A}\right)
C\lambda^2+B\lambda+A=C\left(\lambda+\dfrac{B+\sqrt{B^2-4AC}}{2C}\right)\left(\lambda+\dfrac{B-\sqrt{B^2-4AC}}{2C}\right)
\therefore
Au_{xx}+Bu_{xy}+Cu_{yy}=0
u(x,y)=f_1\left(2Ay+\left(B+\sqrt{B^2-4AC}\right)x\right)+f_2\left(2Ay-\left(B+\sqrt{B^2-4AC}\right)x\right)
u(x,y)=f_1\left(2Cx+\left(B+\sqrt{B^2-4AC}\right)y\right)+f_2\left(2Cx-\left(B+\sqrt{B^2-4AC}\right)y\right)
